  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-agent orchestration with Apollo (Coordinator), Athena (Research Engine), and Hermes (Analyzer)",
    "Dynamic research planning — generates core questions and adapts report structure based on findings",
    "Self-Reflective RAG via Kernel Memory to identify and fill knowledge gaps",
    "Two-stage synthesis: Kernel Memory for section content + large-context LLM (GPT-4.1/Gemini) for final report",
    "Real-time research progress updates via SignalR and .NET channels",
    "Exa AI integration for web search and content retrieval",
    "PostgreSQL + pgvector for vector storage and semantic search",
    "JWT and Google OAuth authentication",
    "Shareable research reports via public links",
    "Dockerized backend deployable to Render.com or Azure"
  ],
